{
  "texts": [
    "One particularly noteworthy DAO in the field of DeSci is VitaDAO.",
    "VitaDAO, aside from being one of the largest communities in DeSci (with 9,472 members in Discord as of September 2023), has also been proven to be remarkably influential in shaping the DeSci landscape.",
    "In early 2023, VitaDAO announced a successful fundraising round, securing $4.1 million from various contributors, including Pfizer Ventures (VitaDAO, 2023b).",
    "This event not only marked the first instance of a DeSci-focused DAO receiving funding from a pharmaceutical company but also the first time a pharmaceutical company actively participated in a DAO's voting process (Cumbers, 2023).",
    "DAOs play a crucial role in the current DeSci movement."
  ]
}